Class NjamsProcessDiagramFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.im.njams.sdk.model.svg.NjamsProcessDiagramFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ProcessDiagramFactory

    public class NjamsProcessDiagramFactory
extends Object
implements ProcessDiagramFactory
    This is the default SDK ProcessDiagramFactory. It converts a ProcessModel into an SVG and give it the default SDK look and feel.

    pnientiedt
